{"tid":304724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師：吳文遠當時已受控　警察涉干犯普通襲擊罪","createTime":"2017-07-01T06:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T23:00:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82ee7cddfc6a32e0e86b2b9b6d28fb86ebe8a615","tid":304724,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:20:59.000Z","msg":"律師黃國桐表示，從有關照片可見，當時吳文遠已遭押上警車，受警方管控，但警員仍涉扯頭髮及疑把他的頭撞向車窗，明顯不當使用武力，「難道吳文遠是馬騮？警方要幫他捉頭蝨？」他續稱，若警方是街頭拘捕期間，有人拒捕，警方使用武力都還可理解，「但現在吳文遠已被押上警車，我看到有何理由警方要這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n黃國桐直指，有關警察的行為已不止不當，且有刑事成份，可能干犯普通襲罪，「仲衰過朱經緯！」據《侵害人身罪條例》，就普通襲擊罪，最高可判處一年監禁"},{"pid":"8fcc1fe57353f40a132f03ebac81f0e42ddf3175","tid":304724,"uid":61488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fc9843822056d02093a58d47efbd80e29a0f73","tid":304724,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"告鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c62f5ce5945e7216566db243de3dea13464d584","tid":304724,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"人力就由得佢"},{"pid":"32cce6691dde360c4f38f7d72a7fa73b128e26ed","tid":304724,"uid":33908,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"告撚到佢踎監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a352419ed8cf6ab4011aba234edbe0da907229d","tid":304724,"uid":80153,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"如果律政司唔告好似都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4e9d759d8d24b28970aec3eb324e4b6d7bd9f5","tid":304724,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"被捕就被捕啦。受控。又用埋D支那話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706160ec37e18419f302cbac